narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: This class is very helpful in reinforcing topics from the lecture class. You do a lot of rock identifying and then get into larger structures later in the semester.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: Strengths: Class helps reinforce topics from lecture class. Has a very reasonable amount of work for a 1/2 credit lab course. Very worth the science credit! Professor is very nice! Weaknesses: Gets very repetitive and slightly boring after a few weeks.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes! Interesting topics, minimal work, pretty easy!
